lead_paragraph: Former French Open finalist Simona Halep took less than 70 minutes to reach the third round of the Wuhan Open, advancing Monday when fellow Romanian Irina-Camelia Begu retired in the second set of their second-round match.

headline.print_headline: Halep Into 3rd Round at Wuhan Open
